      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a basic set of wheels to get you from A to B? This vehicle has plenty of stories to tell and shows significant wear and tear, but it's ready for a new owner who isn't afraid of a little TLC! It's a great opportunity for a mechanic or a DIY enthusiast to roll up their sleeves and bring some life back into a car with character. Sold as-is, this is your chance to grab a bargain!",
