    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This unit features the desirable 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock for optimal power delivery. Critical maintenance has been prioritized, including recent Vanos adjustment and an inspected rear subframe. The chassis retains its signature rigidity, providing exceptional lateral grip and communicative steering feedback. An excellent driver-spec example that balances raw performance with refined engineering.",
